-- U.K. Stocks Decline for a Third  Day as Sage Retreats
-- B y   P e t e r   L e v r i n g
-- 2012-05-09T08:38:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-09/u-k-stocks-decline-for-a-third-day-as-sage-retreats.html
U.K. stocks declined as the benchmark
FTSE 100 index slipped 0.3 percent to 5,540.52 at 9:30 a.m. in
London.  Sixty-three stocks in the 102-member gauge fell as
decliners were led by  Sage Group Plc (SGE) ,  Weir Group Plc (WEIR)  and  Royal
Bank of Scotland Group Plc. (RBS)   To contact the reporter on this story:
